===养老政策===
自2015年5月起，卢甘斯克人民共和国开始以[[俄罗斯卢布|俄罗斯卢布]]的形式支付养老金。 根据卢甘斯克人民共和国领导人[[卢甘斯克人民共和国元首|伊戈尔·普洛尼茨基]]介绍，卢布占85％，[[乌克兰格里夫纳|乌克兰格里夫纳]]占12％，[[美元|美元]]占3％。<ref name="ruble">{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-05-04/forget-tanks-it-s-russia-s-ruble-that-s-conquering-east-ukraine|title=Forget Tanks. Russia's Ruble Is Conquering Eastern Ukraine|author1=Yulia Surkova|author2=Daryna Krasnolutska|lastauthoramp=yes|work=Bloomberg|date=2015-05-04|accessdate=2016-01-12|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101201950/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-05-04/forget-tanks-it-s-russia-s-ruble-that-s-conquering-east-ukraine|dead-url=no}}</ref>乌克兰于2014年12月1日完全停止支付卢甘斯克人民共和国和卢甘斯克人民共和国控制地区的老年人和残疾人养老金。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/donbas-civil-society-leaders-accuse-ukraine-of-declaring-war-on-own-people-371580.html|title=Donbas civil society leaders accuse Ukraine of 'declaring war' on own people|author=Ian Bateson|work=Kyiv Post|date=2014-11-12|accessdate=2016-01-12|archive-date=2015-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911173213/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/donbas-civil-society-leaders-accuse-ukraine-of-declaring-war-on-own-people-371580.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

